Reasoning: The paper deals with the calibration of LiDAR and camera sensors, which is a common problem in robotics and computer vision. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision), followed by cs.RO (Robotics). The use of deep learning and self-supervision suggests that the paper could also be relevant to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the fact that the paper was presented at the Conference on Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (CVPR) suggests that cs.CVPR (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) could also be a relevant category.
